name: KITTY BESPALKO
subtitle: Founder, Stylist, Colorist
summary: Began her career in 2004. Obsessed with creating natural looking reds and blondes, as well as lived in shags, bobs, pixies, and everything in between. When not at the studio, she can be found styling hair for editorial and commercial photoshoots, or weaving on her floor loom.

name: JESSICA CRESS

She specializes in lived-in, long-lasting haircuts and colors with a hand-styled finish.
